{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I had requested slides,"},{"time":3000,"text":"kind of adamantly, \n\n"},{"time":5000,"text":"up till the -- pretty much, last few days,"},{"time":8000,"text":"but was denied access to a slide projector."},{"time":11000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":16000,"text":"I actually find them a lot more emotional --"},{"time":19000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":21000,"text":"-- and personal,"},{"time":24000,"text":"and the neat thing about a slide projector"},{"time":26000,"text":"is you can actually focus the work,"},{"time":29000,"text":"unlike PowerPoint and some other programs."},{"time":34000,"text":"Now, I agree that"},{"time":37000,"text":"you have to -- yeah, there are certain concessions"},{"time":40000,"text":"and, you know, if you use a slide projector,"},{"time":42000,"text":"you're not able to have the bad type"},{"time":45000,"text":"swing in from the back or the side, or up or down,"},{"time":49000,"text":"but maybe that's an O.K. trade-off,"},{"time":52000,"text":"to trade that off for a focus."},{"time":54000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":57000,"text":"It's a thought. Just a thought."},{"time":60000,"text":"And there's something nice about slides getting stuck."},{"time":64000,"text":"And the thing you really hope for"},{"time":66000,"text":"is occasionally they burn up,"},{"time":68000,"text":"which we won't see tonight. So."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72000,"text":"With that, let's get the first slide up here."},{"time":75000,"text":"This, as many of you have probably guessed,"},{"time":78000,"text":"is a"},{"time":80000,"text":"recently emptied beer can in Portugal."},{"time":83000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":86000,"text":"This -- I had just arrived in Barcelona for the first time,"},{"time":90000,"text":"and I thought --"},{"time":92000,"text":"you know, fly all night, I looked up,"},{"time":94000,"text":"and I thought, wow, how clean."},{"time":96000,"text":"You come into this major airport, and they simply have a B."},{"time":101000,"text":"I mean, how nice is that?"},{"time":103000,"text":"Everything's gotten simpler in design,"},{"time":105000,"text":"and here's this mega airport,"},{"time":107000,"text":"and God, I just -- I took a picture."},{"time":109000,"text":"I thought, God, that is the coolest thing I've ever seen at an airport."},{"time":113000,"text":"Till a couple months later,"},{"time":115000,"text":"I went back to the same airport --"},{"time":117000,"text":"same plane, I think -- and looked up,"},{"time":119000,"text":"and it said C."},{"time":121000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":127000,"text":"It was only then that I realized"},{"time":129000,"text":"it was simply a gate that I was coming into."},{"time":132000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":135000,"text":"I'm a big believer in the emotion of design,"},{"time":139000,"text":"and the message that's sent"},{"time":141000,"text":"before somebody begins to read,"},{"time":143000,"text":"before they get the rest of the information;"},{"time":145000,"text":"what is the emotional response they get to the product,"},{"time":148000,"text":"to the story, to the painting -- whatever it is."},{"time":152000,"text":"That area of design interests me the most,"},{"time":154000,"text":"and I think this for me is a real clear,"},{"time":156000,"text":"very simplified version"},{"time":158000,"text":"of what I'm talking about."},{"time":160000,"text":"These are a couple of garage doors painted identical,"},{"time":163000,"text":"situated next to each other."},{"time":165000,"text":"So, here's the first door. You know, you get the message."},{"time":169000,"text":"You know, it's pretty clear."},{"time":171000,"text":"Take a look at the second door and see"},{"time":174000,"text":"if there's any different message."},{"time":176000,"text":"O.K., which one would you park in front of?"},{"time":178000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":180000,"text":"Same color, same message, same words."},{"time":182000,"text":"The only thing that's different"},{"time":184000,"text":"is the expression that the individual door-owner here put into the piece --"},{"time":188000,"text":"and, again,"},{"time":190000,"text":"which is the psycho-killer here?"},{"time":192000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":196000,"text":"Yet it doesn't say that; it doesn't need to say that."},{"time":198000,"text":"I would probably park in front of the other one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"I'm sure a lot of you are aware"},{"time":205000,"text":"that graphic design has gotten a lot simpler in the last"},{"time":207000,"text":"five years or so."},{"time":209000,"text":"It's gotten so simple that it's already starting to kind of"},{"time":211000,"text":"come back the other way again and get a little more expressive."},{"time":214000,"text":"But I was in Milan and saw this street sign,"},{"time":216000,"text":"and was very happy to"},{"time":218000,"text":"see that apparently this idea of minimalism"},{"time":220000,"text":"has even been translated by the graffiti artist."},{"time":224000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":227000,"text":"And this graffiti artist has come along,"},{"time":229000,"text":"made this sign a little bit better, and then moved on."},{"time":232000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":234000,"text":"He didn't overpower it like they have a tendency to do."},{"time":237000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":239000,"text":"This is for a book by \"Metropolis.\""},{"time":243000,"text":"I took some photos, and this is"},{"time":246000,"text":"a billboard in Florida,"},{"time":248000,"text":"and either they hadn't paid their rent,"},{"time":250000,"text":"or they didn't want to pay their rent again on the sign,"},{"time":252000,"text":"and the billboard people were too cheap to tear the whole sign down,"},{"time":255000,"text":"so they just teared out sections of it."},{"time":257000,"text":"And I would argue that it's possibly more effective"},{"time":259000,"text":"than the original billboard in terms of getting your attention,"},{"time":262000,"text":"getting you to look over that way."},{"time":264000,"text":"And hopefully you don't stop and buy those awful pecan things -- Stuckey's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269000,"text":"This is from my second book."},{"time":272000,"text":"The first book is called, \"The End of Print,\""},{"time":275000,"text":"and it was done along with a film,"},{"time":277000,"text":"working with William Burroughs."},{"time":279000,"text":"And \"The End of Print\" is now in its fifth printing."},{"time":282000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":287000,"text":"When I first contacted William Burroughs about being part of it,"},{"time":290000,"text":"he said no; he said he didn't believe it was the end of print."},{"time":294000,"text":"And I said, well, that's fine;"},{"time":296000,"text":"I just would love to have your input on this film and this book,"},{"time":299000,"text":"and he finally agreed to it."},{"time":301000,"text":"And at the end of the film, he says in this great voice"},{"time":305000,"text":"that I can't mimic but I'll kind of try, but not really, he says,"},{"time":308000,"text":"\"I remember attending an exhibition called,"},{"time":311000,"text":"'Photography: The End of Painting.'\""},{"time":315000,"text":"And then he says, \"And, of course, it wasn't at all.\""},{"time":318000,"text":"So, apparently when photography was perfected,"},{"time":321000,"text":"there were people going around saying,"},{"time":324000,"text":"that's it: you've just ruined painting.\n"},{"time":326000,"text":"People are just going to take pictures now."},{"time":329000,"text":"And of course, that wasn't the case."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331000,"text":"So, this is from \"2nd Sight,\""},{"time":333000,"text":"a book I did on intuition."},{"time":335000,"text":"I think it's not the only ingredient in design,"},{"time":337000,"text":"but possibly the most important."},{"time":339000,"text":"It's something everybody has."},{"time":342000,"text":"It's not a matter of teaching it;"},{"time":344000,"text":"in fact, most of the schools tend to discount intuition"},{"time":346000,"text":"as an ingredient of your working process"},{"time":349000,"text":"because they can't quantify it:"},{"time":351000,"text":"it's very hard to teach people the four steps to intuitive design,"},{"time":356000,"text":"but we can teach you the four steps to a nice business card"},{"time":358000,"text":"or a newsletter."},{"time":360000,"text":"So it tends to get discounted."},{"time":362000,"text":"This is a quote from Albert Einstein, who says,"},{"time":366000,"text":"\"The intellect has little to do on the road to discovery."},{"time":370000,"text":"There comes a leap in consciousness --"},{"time":372000,"text":"call it intuition or what you will --"},{"time":375000,"text":"and the solution just comes to you, and you don't know from where or why.\""},{"time":379000,"text":"So, it's kind of like when somebody says, Who did that song?"},{"time":381000,"text":"And the more you try to think about it,"},{"time":383000,"text":"the further the answer gets from you,"},{"time":385000,"text":"and the minute you stop thinking about it,"},{"time":387000,"text":"your intuition gives you that answer, in a sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393000,"text":"I like this for a couple of reasons."},{"time":395000,"text":"If you've had any design courses, they would teach you you can't read this."},{"time":398000,"text":"I think you eventually can and, more importantly, I think it's true."},{"time":401000,"text":"\"Don't mistake legibility for communication.\""},{"time":405000,"text":"Just because something's legible doesn't means it communicates."},{"time":408000,"text":"More importantly, it doesn't mean it communicates the right thing."},{"time":411000,"text":"So, what is the message sent before"},{"time":413000,"text":"somebody actually gets into the material?"},{"time":417000,"text":"And I think that's sometimes an overlooked area."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421000,"text":"This is working with Marshall McLuhan."},{"time":423000,"text":"I stayed and worked with his wife and son, Eric,"},{"time":427000,"text":"and we came up with close to 600 quotes from Marshall"},{"time":432000,"text":"that are just amazing in terms of being ahead of the times,"},{"time":435000,"text":"predicting so much of what has happened"},{"time":437000,"text":"in the advertising, television, media world."},{"time":441000,"text":"And so this book is called \"Probes.\" It's another word for quotes."},{"time":445000,"text":"And it's -- a lot of them are never -- have never been published before,"},{"time":449000,"text":"and basically, I've interpreted the different quotes."},{"time":452000,"text":"So, this was the contents page originally."},{"time":455000,"text":"When I got done it was 540 pages,"},{"time":457000,"text":"and then the publisher, Gingko Press,"},{"time":459000,"text":"ended up cutting it down considerably:"},{"time":462000,"text":"it's just under 400 pages now."},{"time":464000,"text":"But I decided I liked this contents page --"},{"time":467000,"text":"I liked the way it looks -- so I kept it."},{"time":469000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":472000,"text":"It now has no relevance to the book whatsoever,"},{"time":475000,"text":"but it's a nice spread, I think, in there."},{"time":478000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"So, a couple spreads from the book:"},{"time":482000,"text":"here McLuhan says,"},{"time":484000,"text":"\"The new media are not bridges between Man and Nature; they are Nature.\""},{"time":491000,"text":"\"The invention of printing did away with anonymity,"},{"time":493000,"text":"fostering ideas of literary fame"},{"time":496000,"text":"and the habit of considering intellectual effort as private property,\""},{"time":500000,"text":"which had never been done before printing."},{"time":505000,"text":"\"When new technologies impose themselves"},{"time":507000,"text":"on societies long habituated to older technologies,"},{"time":510000,"text":"anxieties of all kinds result.\""},{"time":514000,"text":"\"While people are engaged in creating a totally different world,"},{"time":517000,"text":"they always form vivid images of the preceding world.\""},{"time":525000,"text":"I hate this stuff. It's hard to read."},{"time":528000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":535000,"text":"(Applause)\n"},{"time":538000,"text":"\"People in the electronic age have no possible environment except the globe,"},{"time":545000,"text":"and no possible occupation except information gathering.\""},{"time":549000,"text":"That was it. That's all he saw as the options. And not too far off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553000,"text":"So, this is a project for Nine Inch Nails."},{"time":556000,"text":"And I only show it because it seemed like it got all this relevancy all of a sudden,"},{"time":559000,"text":"and it was done right after 9/11."},{"time":562000,"text":"And I had recently discovered a bomb shelter"},{"time":566000,"text":"in the backyard of a house I had bought in LA"},{"time":569000,"text":"that the real estate person hadn't pointed out."},{"time":572000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":576000,"text":"There was some bomb shelter built, apparently in the '60s Cuban missile crisis."},{"time":580000,"text":"And I asked the real estate guy what it was as we were walking by,"},{"time":583000,"text":"and he goes, \"It's something to do with the sewage system.\""},{"time":585000,"text":"I was, O.K.; that's fine."},{"time":586000,"text":"I finally went down there, and it was this old rusted circular thing,"},{"time":590000,"text":"and two beds, and very kind of creepy and weird."},{"time":593000,"text":"And also, surprisingly, it was done in kind of a cheap metal,"},{"time":596000,"text":"and it had completely rusted through, and water everywhere, and spiders."},{"time":601000,"text":"And I thought, you know, what were they thinking?"},{"time":603000,"text":"You'd think maybe cement, possibly, or something."},{"time":605000,"text":"But anyway, I used this for a cover for the Nine Inch Nails DVD,"},{"time":610000,"text":"and I've also now fixed the bomb shelter with duct tape,"},{"time":616000,"text":"and it's ready. I think I'm ready. So."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"This is an experiment, really, for a client, Quicksilver,"},{"time":628000,"text":"where we were taking what was a six-shot sequence"},{"time":631000,"text":"and trying to use print as a medium to get people to the Web."},{"time":634000,"text":"So, this is a six-shot sequence."},{"time":636000,"text":"I've taken one shot; I cropped it a few different ways."},{"time":640000,"text":"And then the tiny line of copy says,"},{"time":642000,"text":"If you want to see this entire sequence --"},{"time":644000,"text":"how this whole ride was -- go to the website."},{"time":647000,"text":"And my guess is that a lot of the surf kids did go to the site"},{"time":651000,"text":"to get this entire picture."},{"time":654000,"text":"Got no way of tracking it, so I could be totally wrong."},{"time":657000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":660000,"text":"I don't have the site. It's just the piece itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":663000,"text":"This is a group in New York called the Coalition for a Smoke-free Environment --"},{"time":666000,"text":"asked me to do these posters."},{"time":668000,"text":"They were wild-posted around New York City."},{"time":671000,"text":"You can't really -- well, you can't see it at all --"},{"time":673000,"text":"but the second line is really the more kind of payoff, in a sense."},{"time":676000,"text":"It says, \"If the cigarette companies can lie, then so can we.\" But --"},{"time":680000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":683000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":686000,"text":"-- but I did."},{"time":688000,"text":"These were literally wild-posted all over New York one night,"},{"time":692000,"text":"and there were definitely some heads turning,"},{"time":694000,"text":"you know, people smoking and, \"Huh!\""},{"time":696000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":702000,"text":"And it was purposely done to look fairly serious."},{"time":705000,"text":"It wasn't some, you know, weird grunge type or something;"},{"time":708000,"text":"it looked like they might be real. Anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711000,"text":"Poster for Atlantic Center for the Arts, a school in Florida."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714000,"text":"This amazes me. This is a product I just found out."},{"time":717000,"text":"I was in the Caribbean at Christmas,"},{"time":719000,"text":"and I'm just blown away that in this day and age they will still sell --"},{"time":722000,"text":"not that they will sell --"},{"time":725000,"text":"that there is felt a need for people to lighten the color of their skin."},{"time":728000,"text":"This was either an old product with new packaging,"},{"time":730000,"text":"or a brand-new package, and I just thought,"},{"time":733000,"text":"Yikes! How's that still happening?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":736000,"text":"I do a lot of workshops all over the world, really,"},{"time":738000,"text":"and this particular assignment was"},{"time":740000,"text":"to come up with new symbols for the restroom doors."},{"time":743000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":759000,"text":"I felt this was one of the more successful solutions."},{"time":763000,"text":"The students actually cut them up"},{"time":765000,"text":"and put them up around bars and restaurants that night,"},{"time":768000,"text":"and I just always have this vision of this elderly couple going to use the restroom ..."},{"time":772000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":775000,"text":"I did some work for Microsoft a few years back."},{"time":778000,"text":"It was a worldwide branding campaign."},{"time":780000,"text":"And it was interesting to me --"},{"time":782000,"text":"my background is in sociology; I had no design training,"},{"time":785000,"text":"and sometimes people say, well, that explains it --"},{"time":787000,"text":"but it was a very interesting experiment"},{"time":790000,"text":"because there's no product that I had to sell;"},{"time":792000,"text":"it was simply the image of Microsoft they were trying to improve."},{"time":795000,"text":"They thought some people didn't like them."},{"time":798000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":802000,"text":"I found out that's very true,"},{"time":804000,"text":"working on this campaign worldwide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":807000,"text":"And our goal was to try to humanize them a bit,"},{"time":810000,"text":"and what I did was add type and people to the ad,"},{"time":814000,"text":"which the previous campaign had not had,"},{"time":816000,"text":"and nobody remembered them, and nobody referenced them."},{"time":818000,"text":"And we were trying to say that,"},{"time":819000,"text":"hey, some of these guys that work there are actually OK;"},{"time":822000,"text":"some of them actually have friends and family,"},{"time":824000,"text":"and they're not all awful people."},{"time":827000,"text":"And the umbrella campaign was \"Thank God it's Monday.\""},{"time":831000,"text":"So, we tried to take this --"},{"time":833000,"text":"what was perceived as a negative:"},{"time":835000,"text":"their over-competitiveness, their,"},{"time":837000,"text":"you know, long working hours --"},{"time":839000,"text":"and turn it into a positive and not run from it."},{"time":842000,"text":"You know: Thank God it's Monday --"},{"time":843000,"text":"I get to go back to that little cubicle, those fake gray walls,"},{"time":846000,"text":"and hear everybody else's conversations f"},{"time":848000,"text":"or 10 hours and then go home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850000,"text":"But anyway, this is one of the ads I was most pleased with,"},{"time":854000,"text":"because they were all elaborately art-directed,"},{"time":857000,"text":"and this one I thought actually felt like the girl was looking at the computer."},{"time":860000,"text":"It says, \"Wonder Around.\" And then it's a piece of the software."},{"time":863000,"text":"And this is how the ad ran around the world."},{"time":865000,"text":"In Germany, they made one small change without checking with me --"},{"time":869000,"text":"nor did they have to, because it was done through agencies --"},{"time":871000,"text":"but see if you can tell the difference."},{"time":873000,"text":"This is how the ad ran throughout the world;"},{"time":875000,"text":"Germany made one slight change in the ad."},{"time":879000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":883000,"text":"Now, there's kind of two issues here. \n"},{"time":885000,"text":"If you're going to put a kid in the ad, pick one that looks alive."},{"time":889000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":895000,"text":"I just have a feeling this kid's been there for a week, you know."},{"time":897000,"text":"He's just really hoping that boots up and, you know ..."},{"time":900000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":904000,"text":"And then as the agency explained to me, they said,"},{"time":908000,"text":"\"Look, we don't have little green people in our country;"},{"time":911000,"text":"why would we put little green people in our ads, for instance?\""},{"time":914000,"text":"So, I understand their logic. I totally disagree with it;"},{"time":918000,"text":"I think it's a very small-minded approach,"},{"time":920000,"text":"the world is certainly much more global,"},{"time":922000,"text":"and I certainly think the people of Germany"},{"time":924000,"text":"could have handled a little black girl sitting in front of a computer,"},{"time":926000,"text":"though we'll never know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":928000,"text":"This is some work from Ray Gun."},{"time":930000,"text":"And the point of this magazine was to read the articles,"},{"time":933000,"text":"listen to the music, and try to interpret it."},{"time":935000,"text":"There's no grid, there's no system, there's nothing set up in advance."},{"time":939000,"text":"This is an opener for Brian Eno,"},{"time":941000,"text":"and it's just kind of my personal interpretation of the music."},{"time":945000,"text":"This is rockstars talking about teachers they had lusted after in school."},{"time":951000,"text":"There's a lot of great writing in \"Ray Gun.\""},{"time":953000,"text":"And I was fortunate to find a photograph of a teacher sitting on some books."},{"time":957000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":961000,"text":"Article on Bryan Ferry -- just really boring article --"},{"time":963000,"text":"so I set the whole article in Dingbat."},{"time":966000,"text":"(Laughter)\n"},{"time":973000,"text":"You could -- you could highlight it; you could make it Helvetica or something:"},{"time":977000,"text":"it is the actual article."},{"time":979000,"text":"I suppose you could eventually decode it,"},{"time":982000,"text":"but it's really not very well written; it really wouldn't be worthwhile."},{"time":985000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":987000,"text":"Having done a lot of magazines,"},{"time":988000,"text":"I'm very curious how big magazines handle big stories,"},{"time":992000,"text":"and I was very curious to see how Time and Newsweek would handle 9/11."},{"time":996000,"text":"And I was basically pretty disappointed"},{"time":998000,"text":"to see that they had"},{"time":1000000,"text":"chosen to show the photo we'd already seen a million times,"},{"time":1003000,"text":"which was basically the moment of impact."},{"time":1005000,"text":"And People magazine, I thought,"},{"time":1007000,"text":"got probably the best shot."},{"time":1009000,"text":"It's kind of horsey type, but the texture --"},{"time":1013000,"text":"the second plane not quite hitting: \n"},{"time":1015000,"text":"there was something more enticing,"},{"time":1017000,"text":"if that's the right -- it's not the right word --"},{"time":1019000,"text":"but in this cover than Time or Newsweek."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1022000,"text":"But when I got into this magazine,"},{"time":1024000,"text":"there's something kind of disturbing, and this continued."},{"time":1028000,"text":"On the left we see people dying; we see people running for their lives. \n"},{"time":1031000,"text":"And on the right we learn that there's a new way to support your breast."},{"time":1035000,"text":"The coveted right-hand page was not given up to the whole issue."},{"time":1039000,"text":"Look at the image of this lady --"},{"time":1041000,"text":"who knows what she's going through? --"},{"time":1043000,"text":"and the copy says: \"He knows just how to give me goosebumps.\""},{"time":1046000,"text":"Yeah, he jumps out of buildings. It's --"},{"time":1048000,"text":"unfortunately, this one works, kind of, as a spread."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052000,"text":"And this continued through the entire magazine."},{"time":1054000,"text":"It did not let up."},{"time":1056000,"text":"This says: \"One clean fits all.\" ."},{"time":1058000,"text":"There were a lot of orphans made this day,"},{"time":1061000,"text":"and here's a dead body being brought out."},{"time":1063000,"text":"It just seems to me possibly even a blank page"},{"time":1066000,"text":"would have been more appropriate."},{"time":1069000,"text":"And this one I think is possibly the worst:"},{"time":1071000,"text":"two ladies, both facing the same way, both wearing jeans."},{"time":1075000,"text":"One -- who knows what she's going through;"},{"time":1077000,"text":"the other one is worried about model behavior and milk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1082000,"text":"And --"},{"time":1084000,"text":"I gave a talk in New York a couple months after this,"},{"time":1088000,"text":"and afterwards somebody came up to me and they said that --"},{"time":1091000,"text":"they actually emailed me -- and they said that they appreciated the talk,"},{"time":1095000,"text":"and when they got back to their car,"},{"time":1097000,"text":"they found a note on their car that made them think"},{"time":1099000,"text":"maybe New York was getting back to being New York again after this event --"},{"time":1103000,"text":"it had been a few months."},{"time":1105000,"text":"This was what they found on their car."},{"time":1107000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1125000,"text":"There's very few times you'd be happy to find this on your car,"},{"time":1128000,"text":"but it did seem to indicate that we were coming back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1130000,"text":"This is my desktop."},{"time":1132000,"text":"Somebody told me today there was this thing called folders,"},{"time":1135000,"text":"but I don't know what they are."},{"time":1137000,"text":"These are my notes for the talk -- there might be a correlation here."},{"time":1141000,"text":"We are wrapping up. \n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1143000,"text":"This I saw on the plane, flying in, for hot new products."},{"time":1146000,"text":"I'm not sure this is an improvement, or a good idea,"},{"time":1150000,"text":"because, like, if you don't spend quite enough time in front of your computer,"},{"time":1153000,"text":"you can now get a plate in the keyboard,"},{"time":1155000,"text":"so there's no more faking it --"},{"time":1159000,"text":"that you don't really sit at your desk all day and eat and work anyway."},{"time":1163000,"text":"Now there's a plate, and it would be really, really convenient"},{"time":1165000,"text":"to get a piece of pizza, then type a little bit, then ... \n"},{"time":1168000,"text":"I'm just not sure this is improvement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1171000,"text":"If you ever doubt the power of graphic design,"},{"time":1174000,"text":"this is a very generic sign that literally says, \"Vote for Hitler.\" It says nothing else."},{"time":1179000,"text":"And this to me is an extreme case"},{"time":1181000,"text":"of the power of emotion, of graphic design,"},{"time":1184000,"text":"even though, in fact, was a very generic poster at the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1189000,"text":"What's next? What's next is going to be people."},{"time":1191000,"text":"As we get more technically driven,"},{"time":1193000,"text":"the importance of people becomes more than it's ever been before."},{"time":1197000,"text":"You have to utilize who you are in your work."},{"time":1200000,"text":"Nobody else can do that: nobody else can pull from your background,"},{"time":1203000,"text":"from your parents, your upbringing, your whole life experience."},{"time":1206000,"text":"If you allow that to happen, it's really the only way you can do some unique work,"},{"time":1210000,"text":"and you're going to enjoy the work a lot more as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1213000,"text":"This is -- I like found art; hand lettering's coming back in a big way,"},{"time":1216000,"text":"and I thought this was a great example of both."},{"time":1218000,"text":"This lady's advertising for her lost pit bull."},{"time":1220000,"text":"It's friendly -- she's underlined friendly --"},{"time":1223000,"text":"that's probably why she calls it Hercules or Hercles. She can't spell."},{"time":1227000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1230000,"text":"But more importantly,"},{"time":1232000,"text":"she's willing to give you 20 bucks to go find this lost pit bull."},{"time":1235000,"text":"And I'm thinking, yeah, right,"},{"time":1237000,"text":"I'll go look for a lost pit bill for 20 bucks."},{"time":1240000,"text":"I have visions of people going down alleyways yelling out for Hercles,"},{"time":1243000,"text":"and you get charged by this thing and you go,"},{"time":1247000,"text":"oh, please be Hercles; please be the friendly one."},{"time":1249000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1253000,"text":"I'm sure she never found the dog, because I took the sign."},{"time":1256000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1257000,"text":"But I was asked to give a talk at a conference in Sacramento a few years back."},{"time":1261000,"text":"And the theme was courage, and they asked me to talk"},{"time":1263000,"text":"about how courageous it is to be a graphic designer."},{"time":1266000,"text":"And I remembered seeing this photograph of my father,"},{"time":1269000,"text":"who was a test pilot, and he told me that"},{"time":1271000,"text":"when you signed up to become a test pilot,"},{"time":1273000,"text":"they told you that there was a 40 to 50 percent chance"},{"time":1275000,"text":"of death on the job."},{"time":1277000,"text":"That's pretty high for most occupations."},{"time":1280000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1282000,"text":"But, you know, the government would make a plane;"},{"time":1284000,"text":"they'd say, go see if that one flies, would you?"},{"time":1286000,"text":"Some of them did; some of them didn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1289000,"text":"And I started thinking about some of these decisions I have to make"},{"time":1292000,"text":"between, like, serif versus san-serif."},{"time":1295000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1298000,"text":"And for the most part, they're not real life-threatening."},{"time":1302000,"text":"Why not experiment? Why not have some fun?"},{"time":1305000,"text":"Why not put some of yourself into the work?"},{"time":1308000,"text":"And when I was teaching, I used to always ask the students,"},{"time":1310000,"text":"What's the definition of a good job?"},{"time":1312000,"text":"And as teachers, after you get all the answers,"},{"time":1314000,"text":"you like to give them the correct answer."},{"time":1316000,"text":"And the best one I've heard -- I'm sure some of you have heard this --"},{"time":1319000,"text":"the definition of a good job is:"},{"time":1321000,"text":"If you could afford to -- if money wasn't an issue --"},{"time":1325000,"text":"would you be doing that same work?"},{"time":1327000,"text":"And if you would, you've got a great job."},{"time":1330000,"text":"And if you wouldn't, what the heck are you doing?"},{"time":1333000,"text":"You're going to be dead a really long time."},{"time":1335000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]}]}